that the engine experienced a \u201crapid unscheduled disassembly.\u201d</p>\n<p id=\"aNbXGA\"><a href=\"https://www.spacex.com/launches/mission/?missionId=sl-9-3\">SpaceX</a>:</p>\n<blockquote><p id", "id": 856054, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/12/24197332/spacex-falcon-9-in-flight-rocket-failure-starlink-launch", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "source_obj__id": 359, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "SpaceX\u2019s Falcon 9 rockets are grounded after an in-flight failure", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-12T18:57:43+00:00", "description": "<figure>\n      <img alt=\"Illustration showing iPhones on a light blue striped background.\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FMMd4AcCGaKxyOcDWjmM3fN__6g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72025718/236552_Best_iPhone_for_most_people.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption><em>Navigate Apple\u2019s lengthy iPhone product catalog like a pro.</em> | Image: The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n\n  \t\t <p>Whether you want a battery that lasts for days or the very best deal, we\u2019ve got some recommendations for an iPhone you\u2019ll love.</p>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide\">Continue reading&hellip;</a>\n  </p>", "id": 856055, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "source_obj__id": 359, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "The best iPhones", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-12T18:35:57+00:00", "description": "<figure>\n      <img alt=\"Operations At Newport News Shipbuilding Ahead Of Huntington Ingalls Earnings\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/07xR1ECnkBGIPF94WBqGN_wxwmo=/0x0:3500x2333/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73457682/487850445.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption><em>Newport News Shipbuilding, a defense contractor whose shipyard is alleged to have been photographed by drone.</em> | Getty Images</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"FSjn3j\">A foreign graduate student has pleaded guilty to crimes under the Espionage Act for photographing classified US Navy ships with a drone. The case appears to be a first-of-its kind prosecution by the Department of Justice. </p>\n<p id=\"3Jz2lM\">Fengyun Shi, a Chinese citizen and graduate student at the University of Minnesota, was arrested in January after a drone he was flying got stuck in a tree in Newport News, Virginia. A suspicious resident called the police and Shi was questioned before abandoning the drone and fleeing. After t", "id": 856056, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/12/24197356/chinese-national-graduate-student-espionage-act-drone-navy-shipyard-plea-guilty", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "source_obj__id": 359, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Drone photographer pleads guilty to Espionage Act charges", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-12T18:05:59+00:00", "description": "<figure>\n      <img alt=\"Illustration of a hand with a single finger touching an Amazon arrow. Various products float around the edges of the